# Design system only (no arbitrary styling)

Use **only** existing design tokens and Tailwind utilities defined in this project (`src/index.css` + `tailwind.config.ts`).

Do not:

- use arbitrary values (e.g. `p-[...]`, `text-[...]`, `bg-[#...]`)
- use raw colors, `px`, `rem`, or inline styles
- invent new class names or tokens

Examples:

```tsx
// ❌ BAD
<div className="px-[10px] text-[#111]">
  ...
</div>

// ✅ GOOD
<div className="px-3 text-foreground">
  ...
</div>
```
